Creating TestNG Framework 

1. Create a Maven Project
2. Add the dependencies
3. Create your POM (Page object Model)
    
    Pages
    Test
    Utils

4. Create Base class and add the configs (WebDriver / Property Reader)
5. Create Config File    *.properties
6. Create PageInit.
7. Create Common Methods

8. Page Init Extends BaseClass
9. CommonMethods Extends PageInit
10. Create the Page Java file 
11. Add the webelement (PLEASE PLEASE USE CUSTOM XPATH)
12. create the test file and add your test (DONT FORGET THE @Test)